		</span>
	

	<h2 class="story">
		

		

		
		

		

		

		

		<span id="title-174968329" class="story-title"> <a   href="//apple.slashdot.org/story/24/09/10/1559251/apple-must-pay-14-billion-tax-bill-to-ireland-eu-court-rules">Apple Must Pay $14 Billion Tax Bill To Ireland, EU Court Rules</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/business/2024/09/10/apple-ordered-to-pay-13bn-after-losing-eu-tax-battle/"  title="External link - https://www.telegraph.co.uk/business/2024/09/10/apple-ordered-to-pay-13bn-after-losing-eu-tax-battle/" target="_blank"> (telegraph.co.uk) </a></span></span>

		
		
		<!--<span class="comments commentcnt-174968329" >44</span>-->
		

		
		<!-- comment bubble -->
		
			<span class="comment-bubble"><a href="//apple.slashdot.org/story/24/09/10/1559251/apple-must-pay-14-billion-tax-bill-to-ireland-eu-court-rules#comments" title="">44</a></span>
		
	</h2>
	<div class="details" id="details-174968329">
		<span class="story-details">
		<span class="story-views">
			<span class="sodify" onclick="firehose_set_options('color', 'red')" title="Filter Firehose to entries rated red or better"></span><span class="icon-beaker pop1 " alt="Popularity" title="Filter Firehose to entries rated red or better" onclick="firehose_set_options('color', 'red')"><span></span></span> 
		</span>
		</span>
		<span class="story-byline">
	
				
			Posted
				by 
		
		
			
				  msmash
			
		
		

		
		
		<time id="fhtime-174968329" datetime="on Tuesday September 10, 2024 @12:00PM">on Tuesday September 10, 2024 @12:00PM</time>
		
		
			 from the <span class="dept-text">tough-luck</span> dept.
		
		</span>
